messages.content: River Phoenix died during the making of which movie?

response: River Phoenix died during the making of the film **"Dark Blood"**. He passed away on October 31, 1993, before the movie could be completed. At the time of his death, he had also been cast in other projects, but **"Dark Blood"** was the film he was actively working on. The movie was eventually completed and released in 2012 using the existing footage and narration to fill in the missing scenes.
